.checkbox {
	display: inline-flex;
	vertical-align: text-bottom;
	width: 16;
	height: 16;
	background-size: 16px;
	margin-left: 2px;
	margin-right: 5px;
}

.checkbox-on {
	background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2016%2016%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%3E%0A%3Crect%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20fill%3D%22%2358A9D7%22%2F%3E%0A%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M6.71429%2012.2852L14%204.9995L12.7143%203.71436L6.71429%209.71378L3.28571%206.2831L2%207.57092L6.71429%2012.2852Z%22%20fill%3D%22white%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E");
}

.checkbox-off {
	background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2016%2016%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%3E%0A%3Crect%20x%3D%220.75%22%20y%3D%220.75%22%20width%3D%2214.5%22%20height%3D%2214.5%22%20fill%3D%22white%22%20stroke%3D%22%2336352F%22%20stroke-width%3D%221.5%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E");
}
	
</style></head><body><article id="2697a5d8-3064-8041-b97b-eb3fcd7a1152" class="page sans"><header><h1 class="page-title" dir="auto">데이터 추출</h1><p class="page-description" dir="auto"></p><table class="properties"><tbody><tr class="property-row property-row-date"><th><span class="icon property-icon"><img src="https://www.notion.so/icons/calendar_gray.svg" style="width:14px;height:14px;display:block"/></span>날짜</th><td><time>@2025년 9월 8일</time></td></tr><tr class="property-row property-row-multi_select"><th><span class="icon property-icon"><img src="https://www.notion.so/icons/list_gray.svg" style="width:14px;height:14px;display:block"/></span>태그</th><td></td></tr></tbody></table></header><div class="page-body"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2697a5d8-3064-80fe-a175-cd61d73b718f" class="">유튜브 기반 미국 애니메이션 영상 속 wav추출 및 음원 가사화</p></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h1 id="2697a5d8-3064-80b1-aaa7-ef735094c022" class="">🎵 Mood (곡 분위기) 분석</h1></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8063-9334-ddd33f1e75e9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>사용 알고리즘</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80fb-8622-f1ce094575ce" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>librosa</code> 같은 오디오 특징 추출 라이브러리 + 사전 정의된 룰 기반 분류</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-808d-93dd-fc22d909a11d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">또는 <strong>faster-whisper/오디오 feature → lightweight ML 분류기</strong> 조합</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80c8-9291-d191408fe595" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>입력 특징</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80cf-abc8-cb5dafeef2c8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">템포(BPM)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8022-abdf-f17a5f994a72" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">에너지(신호 RMS, spectral centroid)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8097-8c1e-fbfb8d300b9d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">조화 대비(major/minor chroma features)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-808f-84c3-fc6e5b10eef7" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>분류 로직 (예시)</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-801a-b86c-fa2463ff10ef" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">BPM &gt; 100 + 에너지↑ → <em>Excited</em></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-806a-be45-f7313f255080" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">BPM 80~120 + 에너지 중간 → <em>Playful</em></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8033-9849-df4d1d475357" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">BPM &lt; 80 + 에너지↓ → <em>Calm</em></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80a5-90c3-df40384f42e9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">그 사이 값 → <em>Balanced</em></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8087-9992-d8f8e40c7124" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>정확히 말하면</strong>: 딥러닝 모델이 아니라 <strong>signal feature rule-based classifier</strong>에 가까움.</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h1 id="2697a5d8-3064-80b1-8051-d17d0973e8a9" class="">🔁 Repeat Score (반복성 지표)</h1></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80d2-9448-e4f392b802cb" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>사용 알고리즘</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8044-bd1d-c5a9ae4e41fe" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">오디오 신호의 <strong>자기상관(auto-correlation)</strong>, <strong>주기적 스펙트럼 분석</strong></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8075-bd93-c2924a671da6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8086-b9b7-f2d56e695cfd" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:square">가사 텍스트 N-gram 반복률 보정 (자막 있는 경우)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-807a-ad3d-ccc9d1b3cde9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>핵심 아이디어</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ol type="1" id="2697a5d8-3064-801f-8024-de8fe0f0a3e6" class="numbered-list" start="1"><li>오디오 파형을 일정 구간(Window)으로 나눔</li></ol></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ol type="1" id="2697a5d8-3064-80ef-8399-fb55494ec38f" class="numbered-list" start="2"><li>FFT(주파수 변환) 또는 자기상관 → 반복되는 주기 탐색</li></ol></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ol type="1" id="2697a5d8-3064-80cc-a947-cf71ff227d76" class="numbered-list" start="3"><li>주기적 패턴이 뚜렷하면 score ↑</li></ol></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ol type="1" id="2697a5d8-3064-80a3-a4de-dc1e7386db96" class="numbered-list" start="4"><li>score 값은 0~1 사이 (0=무작위, 1=완전 반복)</li></ol></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8054-a015-cfda02e2b2bb" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>실제로 계산된 값 예시</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8088-a27b-eacd80720a5d" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>0.35</code> → 가사/리듬이 꽤 반복적 (아동용 노래에 흔한 구조)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8036-aa74-c1b22a32c26c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>0.15</code> → 반복성 낮음 (스토리텔링 위주 곡)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8030-9dba-ffc98618e0e2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>왜 이렇게 했나?</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8083-a0b1-e78a398be559" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">아이들은 반복되는 구절을 선호하고, 기억도 잘함</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8095-8572-c4b58c07330a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">반복성은 아동용 콘텐츠 성공 요소라 반드시 측정할 필요가 있음</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><p id="2697a5d8-3064-8096-856b-e58398b9c963" class="">
</p></div></div></article><span class="sans" style="font-size:14px;padding-top:2em"></span></body></html>